Gospel awards Mwafaka has released the nominations for this year's edition. Some of the top artistes nominated are Size 8, Bahati, Wahu, Mr Seed, Solomon Mkubwa, Guardian Angel, Evelyn Wanjiru, Mercy Masika and Timeless Noel. This year's theme is "Bringing It Back" and the awards will be held on November 3 at the KICC. Mwafaka Awards recognises, honours and appreciates Kenyan independent gospel music artistes with a positive impact on the industry. The awards are a national recognition of excellence in musical achievements as assessed by Mwafakaâ€™s voting panellists. Held annually, the finest Kenyan gospel artistes are vetted based on artistic and technical merit.